ActCanada Transportation Act
SubjectDAINTY FOODS INC. and 1544929 ONTARIO LTD. ** Agreements **
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Transport enter into AGREEMENTS with DAINTY FOODS INC. and 1544929 ONTARIO LTD. for the purpose of reimbursing business costs incurred by Dainty Foods Inc. and 1544929 Ontario Ltd. as a result of the construction and operation of the international bridge across the DETROIT RIVER between Windsor, Ontario and DETROIT, Michigan.
